    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, a purist-spec example featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This unit delivers linear power delivery to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry is maintained by Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization are excellent. A robust, driver-focused machine ready for the twisties.",
